  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >■Game Summary</h2>Sisters inherit a ranch and mountains from their father's estate. But the island is no longer vibrant.<br>The older sister is a blacksmith in the mountains, and you, the younger sister, are trying to rebuild the ranch and the town.<br>Enjoy a relaxing ranch life with great music.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >■Great music by musicians working in Japan! </h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Music is very important in games. Especially in a lifestyle game, it is important to be relaxing.<br></li><li>We have selected songs by musicians to provide a relaxing gaming experience for everyone. List of musicians.</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >■Gather resources while watching your strength! </h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Gather various resources while eating food, resting early once in a while, and collecting resources.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1944440/extras/ab9966fa0c92b344320b2bc29e13b778.poster.avif?t=1703019217\" width=440 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1944440/extras/ab9966fa0c92b344320b2bc29e13b778.webm?t=1703019217\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1944440/extras/ab9966fa0c92b344320b2bc29e13b778.mp4?t=1703019217\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>.<br><br></li><li>The game has a stamina and satiety level, which gradually decreases as you perform actions.<br></li><li>You can recover them at the restaurant. There is a hot spring in the mountains behind the house, and you can also recover from fatigue in the hot spring.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1944440/extras/8e94c027f1effce34f4951d0de00e9ea.poster.avif?t=1703019217\" width=380 height=290 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1944440/extras/8e94c027f1effce34f4951d0de00e9ea.webm?t=1703019217\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1944440/extras/8e94c027f1effce34f4951d0de00e9ea.mp4?t=1703019217\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>.<br><br></li><li>Croissants for breakfast are especially important. Just by possessing it, you can recover both your strength and satiety every morning.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1944440/extras/91de4ba43c3470325b85f4d0e9b8a39a.poster.avif?t=1703019217\" width=172 height=116 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1944440/extras/91de4ba43c3470325b85f4d0e9b8a39a.webm?t=1703019217\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1944440/extras/91de4ba43c3470325b85f4d0e9b8a39a.mp4?t=1703019217\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>.<br><br></li><li>At 11:00 p.m., you will run out of energy. Try to get home before then.</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >■Grow crops for all seasons! </h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>The items that can be grown in spring, summer, fall, and winter are different. They will not wither, but can be harvested earlier if you water them more.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1944440/extras/4ae5156cb8c75bf0468bb2b294809e22.poster.avif?t=1703019217\" width=440 height=214 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1944440/extras/4ae5156cb8c75bf0468bb2b294809e22.webm?t=1703019217\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1944440/extras/4ae5156cb8c75bf0468bb2b294809e22.mp4?t=1703019217\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>.<br></li><li>Some crops can be harvested again after a few days without re-sowing the seeds.<br></li><li>You can also set up fish cages and mushroom saplings in the hills behind the house, shrimp cages in the sea, and many other things to obtain foodstuffs.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1944440/extras/aeb9176388284c784170d97d86581484.poster.avif?t=1703019217\" width=440 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1944440/extras/aeb9176388284c784170d97d86581484.webm?t=1703019217\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1944440/extras/aeb9176388284c784170d97d86581484.mp4?t=1703019217\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>.<br></li><li>Also, the changes in scenery shown by time and season will delight your visual senses.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1944440/extras/d60779658a4b1ccf2e4f1239a0eb0b73.poster.avif?t=1703019217\" width=370 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1944440/extras/d60779658a4b1ccf2e4f1239a0eb0b73.webm?t=1703019217\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1944440/extras/d60779658a4b1ccf2e4f1239a0eb0b73.mp4?t=1703019217\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>.</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >■Let's go fishing! </h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Fishing is easier in the morning, but becomes more difficult with each hour later in the day.<br></li><li>The items you can catch will differ depending on the location, so try fishing in different places.<br></li><li>You may be able to catch a rare item...?<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1944440/extras/dba0b33a97e9fd967326f9a41c1aa576.poster.avif?t=1703019217\" width=210 height=122 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1944440/extras/dba0b33a97e9fd967326f9a41c1aa576.webm?t=1703019217\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1944440/extras/dba0b33a97e9fd967326f9a41c1aa576.mp4?t=1703019217\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>.</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >■Cooking and blacksmithing! </h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Cooking and blacksmithing based on the items you have collected.<br></li><li>Cooking will greatly restore your strength and satiety, making it an essential item when you are away from home.<br></li><li>Blacksmithing and synthesizing items will allow you to create new items.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1944440/extras/693e57173736311b8f5edaf3495fe4d8.poster.avif?t=1703019217\" width=370 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1944440/extras/693e57173736311b8f5edaf3495fe4d8.webm?t=1703019217\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1944440/extras/693e57173736311b8f5edaf3495fe4d8.mp4?t=1703019217\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>.</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >■Make rice and bread! </h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Brown rice and bread are often used for cooking. These take time to process, so take your time and wait.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1944440/extras/1c1aa0faa27c9907c6178d953baab6bf.poster.avif?t=1703019217\" width=172 height=116 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1944440/extras/1c1aa0faa27c9907c6178d953baab6bf.webm?t=1703019217\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1944440/extras/1c1aa0faa27c9907c6178d953baab6bf.mp4?t=1703019217\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>.</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >■Raise the animals! </h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>You will be able to grow grass, you will be able to have animals. You should raise grass every day.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1944440/extras/1c537457d6780e4f078121a76a2a1ad3.poster.avif?t=1703019217\" width=350 height=264 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1944440/extras/1c537457d6780e4f078121a76a2a1ad3.webm?t=1703019217\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1944440/extras/1c537457d6780e4f078121a76a2a1ad3.mp4?t=1703019217\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>.<br></li><li>Grass can be grown or purchased if you don't have the time.<br></li><li>They produce a harvest, which can be used for a variety of dishes or shipped.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1944440/extras/ed9368348cc509f140cb4fbe5137a594.poster.avif?t=1703019217\" width=380 height=288 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1944440/extras/ed9368348cc509f140cb4fbe5137a594.webm?t=1703019217\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1944440/extras/ed9368348cc509f140cb4fbe5137a594.mp4?t=1703019217\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>.</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >■Make money by shipping! </h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Put your harvest in the shipping area.<br></li><li>At 5:00 p.m., the pickup company will collect your harvest and transfer the money.<br></li><li>If you go to bed before 5:00, the money will be transferred the next morning.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1944440/extras/bc4933b0c57a944ea395ade2f53c633d.poster.avif?t=1703019217\" width=380 height=290 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1944440/extras/bc4933b0c57a944ea395ade2f53c633d.webm?t=1703019217\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1944440/extras/bc4933b0c57a944ea395ade2f53c633d.mp4?t=1703019217\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>.</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >■A new expedition, to a remote island! </h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>As the story progresses and you have more money and ingredients to spare, you will be able to take on the challenge of visiting remote islands.<br></li><li>Monsters will appear here, but you will also be able to get new items.<br></li><li>You may be able to get rare items when you defeat monsters or while searching for items...?<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1944440/extras/71207f0b21a1b23d88323fec01a402e3.poster.avif?t=1703019217\" width=408 height=130 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1944440/extras/71207f0b21a1b23d88323fec01a402e3.webm?t=1703019217\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1944440/extras/71207f0b21a1b23d88323fec01a402e3.mp4?t=1703019217\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>.</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >■Enjoy a slow life that changes from day to day, season to season, and day of the week! </h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Enjoy a slow life with slightly different days, such as animals becoming grumpy without firewood in the winter, or different characters appearing on different days of the week.<br></li><li>Sometimes there will be townspeople who will ask you for a favor.</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >■Game Summary</h2>Sisters inherit a ranch and mountains from their father's estate. But the island is no longer vibrant.<br>The older sister is a blacksmith in the mountains, and you, the younger sister, are trying to rebuild the ranch and the town.<br>Enjoy a relaxing ranch life with great music.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >■Great music by musicians working in Japan! </h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Music is very important in games. Especially in a lifestyle game, it is important to be relaxing.<br></li><li>We have selected songs by musicians to provide a relaxing gaming experience for everyone. List of musicians.</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >■Gather resources while watching your strength! </h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Gather various resources while eating food, resting early once in a while, and collecting resources.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1944440/extras/ab9966fa0c92b344320b2bc29e13b778.poster.avif?t=1703019217\" width=440 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1944440/extras/ab9966fa0c92b344320b2bc29e13b778.webm?t=1703019217\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1944440/extras/ab9966fa0c92b344320b2bc29e13b778.mp4?t=1703019217\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>.<br><br></li><li>The game has a stamina and satiety level, which gradually decreases as you perform actions.<br></li><li>You can recover them at the restaurant. There is a hot spring in the mountains behind the house, and you can also recover from fatigue in the hot spring.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1944440/extras/8e94c027f1effce34f4951d0de00e9ea.poster.avif?t=1703019217\" width=380 height=290 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1944440/extras/8e94c027f1effce34f4951d0de00e9ea.webm?t=1703019217\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1944440/extras/8e94c027f1effce34f4951d0de00e9ea.mp4?t=1703019217\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>.<br><br></li><li>Croissants for breakfast are especially important. Just by possessing it, you can recover both your strength and satiety every morning.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1944440/extras/91de4ba43c3470325b85f4d0e9b8a39a.poster.avif?t=1703019217\" width=172 height=116 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1944440/extras/91de4ba43c3470325b85f4d0e9b8a39a.webm?t=1703019217\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1944440/extras/91de4ba43c3470325b85f4d0e9b8a39a.mp4?t=1703019217\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>.<br><br></li><li>At 11:00 p.m., you will run out of energy. Try to get home before then.</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >■Grow crops for all seasons! </h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>The items that can be grown in spring, summer, fall, and winter are different. They will not wither, but can be harvested earlier if you water them more.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1944440/extras/4ae5156cb8c75bf0468bb2b294809e22.poster.avif?t=1703019217\" width=440 height=214 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1944440/extras/4ae5156cb8c75bf0468bb2b294809e22.webm?t=1703019217\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1944440/extras/4ae5156cb8c75bf0468bb2b294809e22.mp4?t=1703019217\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>.<br></li><li>Some crops can be harvested again after a few days without re-sowing the seeds.<br></li><li>You can also set up fish cages and mushroom saplings in the hills behind the house, shrimp cages in the sea, and many other things to obtain foodstuffs.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1944440/extras/aeb9176388284c784170d97d86581484.poster.avif?t=1703019217\" width=440 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1944440/extras/aeb9176388284c784170d97d86581484.webm?t=1703019217\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1944440/extras/aeb9176388284c784170d97d86581484.mp4?t=1703019217\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>.<br></li><li>Also, the changes in scenery shown by time and season will delight your visual senses.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1944440/extras/d60779658a4b1ccf2e4f1239a0eb0b73.poster.avif?t=1703019217\" width=370 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1944440/extras/d60779658a4b1ccf2e4f1239a0eb0b73.webm?t=1703019217\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1944440/extras/d60779658a4b1ccf2e4f1239a0eb0b73.mp4?t=1703019217\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>.</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >■Let's go fishing! </h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Fishing is easier in the morning, but becomes more difficult with each hour later in the day.<br></li><li>The items you can catch will differ depending on the location, so try fishing in different places.<br></li><li>You may be able to catch a rare item...?<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1944440/extras/dba0b33a97e9fd967326f9a41c1aa576.poster.avif?t=1703019217\" width=210 height=122 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1944440/extras/dba0b33a97e9fd967326f9a41c1aa576.webm?t=1703019217\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1944440/extras/dba0b33a97e9fd967326f9a41c1aa576.mp4?t=1703019217\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>.</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >■Cooking and blacksmithing! </h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Cooking and blacksmithing based on the items you have collected.<br></li><li>Cooking will greatly restore your strength and satiety, making it an essential item when you are away from home.<br></li><li>Blacksmithing and synthesizing items will allow you to create new items.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1944440/extras/693e57173736311b8f5edaf3495fe4d8.poster.avif?t=1703019217\" width=370 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1944440/extras/693e57173736311b8f5edaf3495fe4d8.webm?t=1703019217\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1944440/extras/693e57173736311b8f5edaf3495fe4d8.mp4?t=1703019217\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>.</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >■Make rice and bread! </h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Brown rice and bread are often used for cooking. These take time to process, so take your time and wait.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1944440/extras/1c1aa0faa27c9907c6178d953baab6bf.poster.avif?t=1703019217\" width=172 height=116 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1944440/extras/1c1aa0faa27c9907c6178d953baab6bf.webm?t=1703019217\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1944440/extras/1c1aa0faa27c9907c6178d953baab6bf.mp4?t=1703019217\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>.</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >■Raise the animals! </h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>You will be able to grow grass, you will be able to have animals. You should raise grass every day.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1944440/extras/1c537457d6780e4f078121a76a2a1ad3.poster.avif?t=1703019217\" width=350 height=264 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1944440/extras/1c537457d6780e4f078121a76a2a1ad3.webm?t=1703019217\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1944440/extras/1c537457d6780e4f078121a76a2a1ad3.mp4?t=1703019217\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>.<br></li><li>Grass can be grown or purchased if you don't have the time.<br></li><li>They produce a harvest, which can be used for a variety of dishes or shipped.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1944440/extras/ed9368348cc509f140cb4fbe5137a594.poster.avif?t=1703019217\" width=380 height=288 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1944440/extras/ed9368348cc509f140cb4fbe5137a594.webm?t=1703019217\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1944440/extras/ed9368348cc509f140cb4fbe5137a594.mp4?t=1703019217\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>.</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >■Make money by shipping! </h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Put your harvest in the shipping area.<br></li><li>At 5:00 p.m., the pickup company will collect your harvest and transfer the money.<br></li><li>If you go to bed before 5:00, the money will be transferred the next morning.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1944440/extras/bc4933b0c57a944ea395ade2f53c633d.poster.avif?t=1703019217\" width=380 height=290 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1944440/extras/bc4933b0c57a944ea395ade2f53c633d.webm?t=1703019217\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1944440/extras/bc4933b0c57a944ea395ade2f53c633d.mp4?t=1703019217\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>.</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >■A new expedition, to a remote island! </h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>As the story progresses and you have more money and ingredients to spare, you will be able to take on the challenge of visiting remote islands.<br></li><li>Monsters will appear here, but you will also be able to get new items.<br></li><li>You may be able to get rare items when you defeat monsters or while searching for items...?<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1944440/extras/71207f0b21a1b23d88323fec01a402e3.poster.avif?t=1703019217\" width=408 height=130 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1944440/extras/71207f0b21a1b23d88323fec01a402e3.webm?t=1703019217\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1944440/extras/71207f0b21a1b23d88323fec01a402e3.mp4?t=1703019217\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>.</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >■Enjoy a slow life that changes from day to day, season to season, and day of the week! </h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Enjoy a slow life with slightly different days, such as animals becoming grumpy without firewood in the winter, or different characters appearing on different days of the week.<br></li><li>Sometimes there will be townspeople who will ask you for a favor.</li></ul>",
